    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Balloons anchored to the ground and grouped as protective screens to prevent or hinder operations by enemy aircraft.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
